column44:
I was just practicing what I'd do
if the Rampage came. You know,
running through the steps and stuff.

And honestly, Magnamalo scares me;
I thought the worst we'd encounter
would be like some Bombadgy...

column47:
Angeblich ist eine Art Schlange aufgetaucht;
eine, die selbst Meister Hojo noch nie
gesehen hat.

column53:
Os vendedores de arroz, Senari e
Suzukari, são um casal tão doce;
estão sempre apoiando um ao outro.
